latestPosts.caption:
Parenthood is the most wonderful experience of our lives where we welcome our self in another expression✨

A short note to all parents:
Don’t aim to make your child a “doctor”, “engineer”, “lawyer” or anything! Your child is the unique expression of the infinite spirit of love, joy, abundance and wisdom. You are welcoming yourself and what can be more blissful than this! Don’t teach them to struggle in their own existence, instill fear or insecurities in them and please do not worry for them, it’s never a sign of care! They are the perfect expression of the perfect divine existence who is all powerful ✨ Their every desire is already present in their heart and you are his/her first guide and best friend to unleash that. Just be that guide without being attached to them and without any expectations from them.. They are here in creation to create magnificent creations that enriches the whole of existence. Your role is minimal yet the most profound ❤️

This post is about YOU.  For ages you have been separated from yourself identified with many expressions.  The world taught you to keep your self concept low as a gesture of false humility.  You are not “any other” beautiful woman or handsome man. You are the only one divine existence and your expression is absolutely precious and unique.  You are the best, the highest and eternal miracle called life.Embrace your highest glory. latestPosts.caption:
Today I heard some people discussing strategy at the cafe. For years I didn’t realise why I never grasped empty concepts and strategies! The world said you will fall behind if you don’t use your rational mind. Somehow years passed in this world of shadow until one day that which I held so dear to my heart, the meaning of love completely had gone for a toss and I was dying(not which the world calls death). That which I thought was love was nothing but what was taught to me…  Then I found love as my universal essence which I was falsely searching outside me!  I found out light at the end of the tunnel.  Bliss at the end of suffering.
Wisdom at the end of illusion.
Life at the end of death..
Finally I overcame death and was born into eternity, realising I am life and the light of existence, the entire journey was within..✨ I wish you all life, which is nothing but absolute love, joy, bliss, wisdom, abundance.  Wearing this beautiful dress from @virgio.official #lifepost #lifeisbeautiful #existence #bliss
